<title>Navbar Example: Vertical Sidebar</title>
<style>
  .sidebar-layout { display: flex; min-height: 80vh; }
  .sidebar-content { flex: 1; padding: 2rem; }
  .sidebar-nav { width: 250px; min-width: 250px; }
</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="sidebar-layout">
  <%# ========== VERTICAL SIDEBAR NAVBAR (dark, bg-dark) ========== %>
  <div class="sidebar-nav">
    <%- passData.plugin.bootstrapNavbar.render({name: 'sidebar'}, passData) %>
  </div>

  <div class="sidebar-content">
    <h1>Vertical Navbar - Sidebar</h1>

    <div class="card mt-3">
      <div class="card-header">Caratteristiche di questo esempio</div>
      <div class="card-body">
        <ul>
          <li><strong>type:</strong> <code>vertical</code></li>
          <li><strong>colorScheme:</strong> <code>dark</code></li>
          <li><strong>bgClass:</strong> <code>bg-dark</code></li>
          <li><strong>position:</strong> <code>start</code> (sidebar a sinistra)</li>
          <li><strong>sections.left:</strong> parte superiore della sidebar</li>
          <li><strong>sections.right:</strong> parte inferiore (separata da <code>&lt;hr&gt;</code>)</li>
          <li><strong>Auth items:</strong> "Users" visibile solo per admin, "Settings" e "Logout" condizionali</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card mt-3">
      <div class="card-header">Codice EJS</div>
      <div class="card-body">
        <pre><code>&lt;div class="sidebar-layout"&gt;
  &lt;div class="sidebar-nav"&gt;
    &lt;%- passData.plugin.bootstrapNavbar.render({name: 'sidebar'}, passData) %&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class="sidebar-content"&gt;
    &lt;!-- contenuto pagina --&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</code></pre>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card mt-3">
      <div class="card-header">Note</div>
      <div class="card-body">
        <p>Il layout sidebar richiede un wrapper flex. Nel type <code>vertical</code>:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><code>sections.left</code> = items nella parte alta</li>
          <li><code>sections.right</code> = items nella parte bassa (separati da &lt;hr&gt;)</li>
          <li>I dropdown funzionano anche in verticale</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="mt-3"><a href="/navbarExamples/">&larr; Tutti gli esempi</a></p>
  </div>
</div>

